NK063(gu)004:1: // dpal gsang ba snying po'i bsdus don 'od zer mtha' yas zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK063(gu)004:3: thugs mchog rdo rje mi bskyod la //
NK063(gu)004:4: lhag pa'i lha phyir phyag btsal nas //
NK063(gu)004:5: rgyud don la dbye de bsdus don //
NK063(gu)004:6: bde blag rtog phyir 'dir dgod bya //
NK063(gu)004:7: dpal gsang ba'i snying po 'di la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:8: rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:9: mtshan de dang ldan pa'i rgyud don dngos so //
NK063(gu)004:11: klad kyi don ston pa la phyag btsal ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:12: gzhung gi don yi ge'i rgyud bshad pa dngos dang /
NK063(gu)004:13: mjug gi don rgyud rdzogs pa'i bya ba bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:15: bka' rang gnyer gzhung tshogs le'u nyer gnyis la /
NK063(gu)004:16: slob dpon gdams ngag gis lnga ste /
NK063(gu)004:17: rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:20: de dag la khyab byed du rgyud kyi dgos 'brel dang /
NK063(gu)004:21: 'khor la rgyud gdams shing gtad pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:22: dang po rgyud kyi rgyu gleng gzhi la gnyis /
NK063(gu)004:26: thun mong ma yin pa'i sgo nas gleng gzhi mdor bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:27: de rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:35: ston pa'i ngo bo'i 'chad pa'i skyes bu dang mtshan thun mong du bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:62: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)004:63: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)004:67: rigs khyad par can gyi la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:71: nang gi sems dpa' yab yum dang /
NK063(gu)004:72: phyi'i sems dpa' yab yum mo //
NK063(gu)004:76: gleng gzhi bsdus pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:77: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:78: bsdus pa dngos gleng gzhi'i nges tshig dang bcas pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:79: gsang sngags mtshon par byed pa'i tshig go //
NK063(gu)004:80: don gnyis pa rkyen gleng bslang ba la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:84: gzhung dngos gleng bslang ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:87: thun mong ma yin par gleng bslang ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:91: dbang gnyis kyi las thun mong du bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:93: gleng bslang nas dbang bskur ba dngos dang /
NK063(gu)004:94: gsang dbang thob pa'i yon tan nges tshig dang bcas pa pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:96: dbang bskur ba'i ched du yab yum gyis snyoms par zhugs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:97: nyams su bstar ba'i don las rdzas kyis dbang bskur zhing de'i rtogs pa brjod pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:98: dbang gnyis kyi las la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:99: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:100: sems bskyed cing ji ltar dbang bskur ba'i rim pa dngos dang /
NK063(gu)004:108: thun mong du gleng bslang ba la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:112: lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:113: gsang ba bzhis chod pa'i gdul bya'i ched du rgyud bshad par zhus pa dngos so //
NK063(gu)004:114: ston pas gnang ba la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:115: thugs rje bskyed nas gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:116: lhun grub kyi chos ston pa'i ched du spro bar zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:117: gsum pa rgyud don le'u gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:124: bstan pa 'byung ba'i spyi'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK063(gu)004:125: yongs su shes par bya ba rgyud dngos kyi lta ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:135: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdzad pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:141: nyon mongs pa la dgongs te dbye ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:142: gnyen po la dgongs te bsdu ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:143: yongs su shes par bya ba rgyud dngos kyi lta ba la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:144: ston pas gsungs te sdud pa pos lo rgyus su brjod de mtshams sbyar ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:145: ji ltar gtan la dbab bya'i lta ba dngos so //
NK063(gu)004:147: gtan la dbab bya 'khor ba'i chos dang /
NK063(gu)004:148: 'bebs byed mya ngan las 'das pa theg pa chen po'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)004:152: grub mtha'i 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:155: thun mong ma yin pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK063(gu)004:160: rgyu gcig pa'i rtogs pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:162: mya ngan las 'das pa'i theg pa la lnga ste /
NK063(gu)004:165: sangs rgyas dang chos la 'byung 'jig dar nub med pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:167: gdul bya dang mthun par gsungs pa'ang yang dag par gsung du med par bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:168: rgyud kyi che ba la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:169: bstan pa'i 'byung gnas yin pa dang //
NK063(gu)004:172: le'u bsdus pa la bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)004:173: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:175: gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig dang /
NK063(gu)004:177: le'u bzhi pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:178: gsungs pa lo rgyus su rjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:185: yi ge ji ltar byung ba'i tshul dang /
NK063(gu)004:186: yi ge byung ba'i mthu dang /
NK063(gu)004:187: lam pa'i dbang du sems sbyang ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:189: sems sbyang ba la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:190: a la sems sbyang ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:191: yi ge gzhan la sems sbyang ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:192: de ye shes kyi rgyur bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:193: don bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:194: lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:198: spyi'i mtshan nyid kyi don dang /
NK063(gu)004:199: rang gi mtshan nyid kyi don no //
NK063(gu)004:206: yi ge sku gsum gyi bdag nyid du sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:207: sangs rgyas de dag gi sku gsung thugs kyi mtshon byed du bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:209: don bden pa dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin chos skur dang /
NK063(gu)004:210: yi ge bsdus pa'i chos thams cad la dbang sgyur ba longs sku dang /
NK063(gu)004:211: de nyid sna tshogs su snang bas don mdzad pa sprul skur bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:216: rang gi mtshan nyid la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:217: khyab byed kyi yi ge gsum gyi dang /
NK063(gu)004:218: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi don bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:220: kun tu bzang mo'i yi ge dang /
NK063(gu)004:221: rigs lnga yab yum gyi dang /
NK063(gu)004:222: sems dpa' sgo ba dang bcas pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:226: byang gi sgo ba'i yi ge'o //
NK063(gu)004:227: sems dpa' sgo ba dang bcas pa la bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)004:228: nang gi sems dpa' shar gyi sgo ba dang bcas pa'i yi ge dang /
NK063(gu)004:229: nang gi sems ma lho'i sgo ba dang bcas pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)004:230: phyi sems dpa' nub kyi sgo ba dang bcas pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)004:233: lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:237: le'u lnga pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:238: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:243: de la mnyes pa'i tshul gyis mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:249: de nyid thams cad du rang snang ba dang //
NK063(gu)004:250: de las dkyil 'khor bsgom pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:251: des kar dag pas blang dor dang bral ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:252: de la 'dris par bslabs pas dngos grub 'grub pa'i tshul lo //
NK063(gu)004:254: gdams pa nye bar bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:255: ji ltar gtan la dbab pa dngos so //
NK063(gu)004:256: tha ma'i grub tshul la gnyis te //
NK063(gu)004:260: thun mong gi dngos grub dang /
NK063(gu)004:265: le'u drug pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:275: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa sku'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)004:279: dkyil 'khor gyi tshad dam che ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:281: ngo bo rgyan dang bcas pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:284: bzhugs tshul bzhugs gnas dang bcas pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:286: sku mdog tshul dang bcas pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:287: rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor la bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)004:291: de gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)004:294: sngags kyi lam gyis 'grub tshul lo //
NK063(gu)004:296: sgrib pa sbyong zhing 'bras bu thob tshul dang /
NK063(gu)004:297: des thob pa 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsum mo //
NK063(gu)004:298: sngags kyi 'grub tshul la'ang gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:299: 'grub tshul sangs rgyas kyi sa gnyis dang /
NK063(gu)004:300: grub pa'i ngo bo sku lngar bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:304: gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig go //
NK063(gu)004:305: le'u bdun pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:310: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK063(gu)004:311: rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)004:313: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i sngags dang /
NK063(gu)004:314: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang ba'i sngags dang /
NK063(gu)004:317: rten gzhal yas bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:318: brten pa lha bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:319: dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:321: rigs lnga yab yum bskyed pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)004:322: sems dpa' yab yum gyi dang /
NK063(gu)004:323: sgo ba yab yum gyi dang /
NK063(gu)004:324: kun tu bzang po yab yum gyi dang /
NK063(gu)004:325: thub pa drug bskyed pa'i sngags so //
NK063(gu)004:327: nang gi sems dpa' yab yum gyi dang /
NK063(gu)004:328: phyi'i sems dpa' yab yum mo //
NK063(gu)004:329: dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa la gsum /
NK063(gu)004:335: byin gyis brlab pa'i sngags so //
NK063(gu)004:336: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang ba la lnga ste /
NK063(gu)004:339: rig pa'i me tog dor ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:342: rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:345: rnam grangs pa'i sgos nas mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:349: rig pa byin gyis rlabs kyi dang /
NK063(gu)004:351: tshangs pa dbyangs kyi gsung ngo //
NK063(gu)004:352: le'u brgyad pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:357: rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK063(gu)004:358: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK063(gu)004:360: phyag rgya spros pa dang bcas pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK063(gu)004:361: phyag rgya rnam grangs bsdus pa'i sgo nas mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:362: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya la gnyis /
NK063(gu)004:366: rigs lnga spyi'i dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK063(gu)004:369: rigs lnga yab yum gyi dang /
NK063(gu)004:370: sems dpa' yab yum gyi dang /
NK063(gu)004:371: sgo ba yab yum gyi dang /
NK063(gu)004:373: kun bzang yab yum gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK063(gu)004:374: phyag rgya spros pa dang bcas pa la gnyis /
NK063(gu)004:375: snang ba rnam 'byed la ji ltar bslab pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:377: le'u dgu pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:386: phra mo la blo sbyangs pa'i ru yis bsnyen pa bya ba las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:387: dkyil 'khor gyi las kyi rim pa dngos bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:390: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor zhi ba ltar dang /
NK063(gu)004:391: mchog gi dkyil 'khor yang zhi ba ltar shes par gdams pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:410: byin gyis brlabs la gdab pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:416: stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:417: rol mo lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:418: ting nge 'dzin gnyis kyis sbyangs shing bskyed pa'i yon tan dang /
NK063(gu)004:419: ye shes can gzhug pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:422: phyi nang gi mchod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:423: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:424: gsang ba'i mchod pa bya ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:426: slob dpon dang slob ma 'jug pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:427: slob ma la lha bsgom par nan tan bya ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:429: dbang gi rgyu yon dbul ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:430: snod dang sbyar la bskur ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:435: gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor la gnyis /
NK063(gu)004:446: gnas skabs su tshe dbang 'grub pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:447: mthar thug tu sku lnga 'grub pa'i dus so //
NK063(gu)004:450: de ltar grub pa'i 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo dngos so //
NK063(gu)004:452: 'grub tshul rang snang du bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:453: de dpe'i sgo nas bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:454: rang gi ngo bo la gsum /
NK063(gu)004:455: rgyu rkyen las ma skyes shing don byed nus pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:456: gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i don rang byung gi ye shes su bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:457: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gdul bya gzigs tshul lo //
NK063(gu)004:458: le'u bcu pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:463: dbang bskur ba'i rim pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:464: de ma bskur ba'i skyon dang /
NK063(gu)004:469: zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:470: le'u bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa sdeb nas tshogs sgrub pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:471: lo rgyus su brjod pa gnyis dang /
NK063(gu)004:475: tshogs bsgrub pa'i phyir gzhung gnyis sdeb pa dngos dang /
NK063(gu)004:483: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK063(gu)004:486: grub mtha' 'bras bu gzhan du zhen pa dgag pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:490: mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs so //
NK063(gu)004:495: gang bsgrub pa'i gzhung phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:496: ji ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:499: gnas dang yo byad thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:501: bsgrub pa'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:503: khro ba'i sgo nas bsgrub pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:514: bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:516: tshom bu gcig pa la dang /
NK063(gu)004:518: lnga pa la bsnyen pa bya ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:519: nye ba'i bsnyen pa dang sgrub pa thun mong du bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:520: rnal 'byor pas bye brag tu bsgom pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:521: tshom bu'i lha bsgrub pa'i thabs dngos so //
NK063(gu)004:523: tshom bu gcig pa bsgrub pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:526: sgrub pa chen po la gnyis te //
NK063(gu)004:527: sgrub byed yo byad la ji ltar spyad pa'i thabs dang /
NK063(gu)004:528: de'i bsgrub bya dngos grub kyi don dngos so //
NK063(gu)004:530: yo byad bzhi la spyad thabs dang /
NK063(gu)004:531: +aa li k+aa li la spyad thabs so //
NK063(gu)004:533: +aa li sbyor ba la spyad thabs dang /
NK063(gu)004:534: k+aa li sgrol ba la spyad thabs dang /
NK063(gu)004:535: de ltar spyad par sgrub pa la rtsod pa'i skyon spong ba dang bcas pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:537: spyad par bya ba'i yul dang /
NK063(gu)004:538: ji ltar spyad pa'i thabs dang /
NK063(gu)004:539: dngos grub chen po yum gyi mkha' nas blang ba'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)004:542: dkyil 'khor gyi bkod pa rdzas kyi dngos grub dngos so //
NK063(gu)004:543: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:547: yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i 'bras bu dang /
NK063(gu)004:548: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi cha lugs dang /
NK063(gu)004:549: mthar thug pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:550: le'u bcu gsum pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:551: lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:556: de gsungs pa'i tshul gyis mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:558: mtshon par byed pa'i sgo dang /
NK063(gu)004:559: myong bar byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK063(gu)004:560: mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu dang //
NK063(gu)004:561: rgyud 'di la mos pa tsam gyi yon tan dang /
NK063(gu)004:562: 'di snod dang ldan pa'i yul la bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:563: man ngag gi che ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:564: snod ldan la sbyin zhing snod ngan la byin pa'i nyes dmigs so //
NK063(gu)004:566: mtshon bya theg pa'i sgo dang /
NK063(gu)004:567: de ji ltar mtshon pa'i thabs so //
NK063(gu)004:568: myong bar byed pa'i thabs la gdams ngag gis lnga las /
NK063(gu)004:569: lta ba rtogs nas dang por de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:570: de nas snying rje chen po'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:571: de nas phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:572: de nas spros pa bsgom pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:573: de nas tshogs sgrub pas 'bras bu rang la snang
NK063(gu)004:574: tshul dang lngas phyi shes rab grol lam gyi dbang
NK063(gu)004:575: du bshad pa'o // gzhung de nyid la yang /
NK063(gu)004:576: kun tu bzang po'i thig le bsgom pa'i man ngag dang /
NK063(gu)004:579: khyab gdal chen po'i man ngag dang bzhis thabs lam gdams ngag steng sgo'i dbang du bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:581: thabs nyid shes rab tu sbyor ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:582: shes rab nyid thabs su sbyor ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:583: thabs shes rab dbyer med du sbyor ba dang gsum gyis gsang ba 'og sgo'i dbang du bshad pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:584: mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu la gnyis /
NK063(gu)004:593: des mthar thug pa'i 'bras bu la sbyor tshul lo //
NK063(gu)004:594: mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu la gnyis /
NK063(gu)004:596: gzhan don mdzad pa'i tshul lo //
NK063(gu)004:597: man ngag gi che ba la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:598: rgyal ba'i gshegs bshul yin pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:599: rnal 'byor pa'i lam yin pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:601: le'u bcu bzhi pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:611: de dag la spyir bstod pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:612: le'u bco lnga pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:616: gang gdul bya gtso bo ji ltar btul ba dgos ched kyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK063(gu)004:617: 'khor gyi mkha' 'gro dam la btags te ming gi dbang bskur nas mu ran la bkod tshul lo //
NK063(gu)004:619: gang gis 'dul byed kyi gnyen po dang /
NK063(gu)004:621: ji ltar 'dul thabs kyi phrin las dang /
NK063(gu)004:627: spyir sems can thams cad gol ba'i dang /
NK063(gu)004:628: bye brag tu ru tra gol ba'i rgyu'o //
NK063(gu)004:634: yi dwags su skye ba blangs pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:635: rgyu mthun pa la gnyis te /
NK063(gu)004:636: skye ba blangs pa dngos dang /
NK063(gu)004:637: de'i lus dang mthu'i mtshan nyid bstan pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:639: thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs rjes gzigs nas 'dul ba mdor dang /
NK063(gu)004:643: che mchog longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK063(gu)004:645: sprul pa rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK063(gu)004:646: byin gyis rlabs kyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK063(gu)004:648: sprul pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK063(gu)004:649: phrin las rmad du byung ba'i ngo bo dang /
NK063(gu)004:651: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK063(gu)004:653: ngo mtshar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK063(gu)004:659: de ltar btul ba'i 'bras bu la bzhi ste /
NK063(gu)004:660: dbang bskur te gnas spar bas snang ba rnam par 'byed pa thob pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:661: dam bcas nas lus gdan du phul ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:664: le'u bcu drug pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:665: lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:669: gsung gi dkyil 'khor mngon du phyung ba dngos dang /
NK063(gu)004:672: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i sngags dang /
NK063(gu)004:673: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs pa la sogs pa las kyi rim pa'i sngags so //
NK063(gu)004:675: rigs lnga yab yum bcu'i rtsa ba bskyed pa las dang bcas pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)004:676: khro mo nyi shu rtsa ba bskyed pa las dang bcas pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)004:677: dbang phyug ma nyer brgyad kyi rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags so //
NK063(gu)004:678: khro mo nyi shu'i sngags la gsum /
NK063(gu)004:679: gnas ma brgyad bskyed pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)004:680: yul ma brgyad bskyed pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)004:681: sgo ma bzhi bskyed pa'i sngags so //
NK063(gu)004:682: las kyi rim pa'i sngags la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:683: snyan gsan dbab cing spyan drang ba'i sngags dang /
NK063(gu)004:684: rig pa'i me tog dor zhing dngos grub bskul ba'i dang /
NK063(gu)004:685: drin lan du mchod cing bstim pa'i sngags so //
NK063(gu)004:686: le'u bcu bdun pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:687: lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:691: sku'i dkyil 'khor mngon du phyung ba dngos dang /
NK063(gu)004:697: gzhal yas khang gi ngo bo rgyan dang bcas pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:707: le'u bco brgyad pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:708: lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:713: de gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)004:720: gti mug dam rdzas kyi dang /
NK063(gu)004:721: 'dod pa yon tan gyi mchod pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:722: le'u bcu dgu pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:723: lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:730: dam tshig gi che ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:731: rnam grangs mdor bstan pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:732: mnyam pa'i dam tshig gi skyon yon dang bcas pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:733: dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon dang /
NK063(gu)004:734: dam tshig gi rang bzhin dang /
NK063(gu)004:735: dam tshig gi rnam grangs rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:736: de ma nyams pa'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)004:742: ma byin par len pa'i dang /
NK063(gu)004:744: mi tshangs par spyod pa'i dam tshig 'dus la dag pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:745: rnam grangs mdor bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:747: yan lag gi dam tshig dang /
NK063(gu)004:748: nyams pa'i skyon gyis de las 'da' bar dka' ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:752: yan lag nyams pa'i skyon no //
NK063(gu)004:753: rnam grangs rgyas pa la gnyis /
NK063(gu)004:754: sum brgya drug cur dbye ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:755: gdul bya la dgongs te dbye ba'o //
NK063(gu)004:756: le'u nyi shu pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:757: lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:762: de gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)004:765: lu gu rgyud kyi glu bro'i sgo nas phrin las bya ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:767: bro gar glu tshig gi yon tan dang /
NK063(gu)004:775: de bzhi char la lnga lnga ste /
NK063(gu)004:777: drag po'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:779: mchod sbyin bya ba yon tan dang bcas pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:780: lu gu rgyud kyi bro'i las yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:785: dam tshig bsgrag cing las la bskul ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:786: las de ma bsgrubs pa'i skyon dang /
NK063(gu)004:787: las bsgrubs pa'i yon tan no //
NK063(gu)004:788: bro gar glu tshig bstan pa la drug ste /
NK063(gu)004:789: khrag 'thung yab yum kyi glu tshig gis las bzhi ka 'grub pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:790: phyogs kyi khro mos dbang dang rgyas pa 'grub pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:791: mtshams kyi khro mos zhi drag 'grub pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:792: phyogs kyi phra men mas drag po 'grub pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:793: mtshams kyi phra men gyis kyang drag po 'grub pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:794: dbang phyug mas pho nya dang mngag gzhug gi las thams cad 'grub pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:795: le'u nyer gcig pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:796: lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:808: dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:809: spyi don lnga pa rgyud gdams shing gtad pa la gsum ste /
NK063(gu)004:810: sdud pa pos gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod de mtshams sbyar ba dang /
NK063(gu)004:814: rang bzhin gyi rgyud ye nas sangs rgyas pa las mi 'gyur bas 'bod cig par gdams pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:815: bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par bya ba'i phyir mtshon byed kyi rgyud gtad pa dngos so //
NK063(gu)004:817: lhan cig pa'i 'khor sdud pa po la gtad pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:818: go phye ba'i 'khor gang zag chos mig can la gtad pa dang /
NK063(gu)004:819: nges par lung bstan pa'i sgo nas gtad pa'i 'thad pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK063(gu)004:820: mjug gi don rgyud rdzogs pa'i bya ba la gsum /
NK063(gu)004:821: rgyud kyi mdzad pa rdzogs nas dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid la bzhugs tshul dang /
NK063(gu)004:822: che ba dang ldan pa gsang ba bstan pa'i rgyud kyi khungs dang /
NK063(gu)004:823: yongs su mi nub pa'i phyir 'di las thams cad
NK063(gu)004:824: spros te chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba las 'bras
NK063(gu)004:826: dpal gsang ba snying po'i bsdus don 'od zer mtha'
NK063(gu)004:827: yas zhes bya ba dpal sman lung du mi bskyod
